AUDIENCE: Thank you.

00:52:49.410 --> 00:52:51.110
This is on a slightly
lighter note.

00:52:51.110 --> 00:52:51.610
SALMAN RUSHDIE: Yes.

00:52:51.610 --> 00:52:52.818
CHRISTINA MATTEOTTI: Oh good.

00:52:52.818 --> 00:52:53.430
